race.comment: MILE A MINUTE (2) has been a in top form recording back to back wins and both in best of the card, going 18.86 two back before 19.03 last time. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Form reads well for this. WINKING WILLIE (1) finished well back at this track last time when a 3.5 lengths fifth (16.89) but back to the course now of his latest success. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to his credit. Bold showing expected. CATCH SOME RAYS (7) boasts a strong record this journey here with 10 wins and three minors from 24 tries. In the money last time at this track (19.06) in a Free For All, finishing a half a length second. Can feature with the right run. FLAMING FOX (3) warrants respect following a recent placing over this course and distance.
